title: THURSDAY - TNF PREVIEW CARDINALS/SEAHAWKS 2020
itunes:title: THURSDAY - TNF PREVIEW CARDINALS/SEAHAWKS 2020
description:
It's a massive NFC West showdown (:07) as the Cardinals take on the Seahawks in Thursday Night Football...We'll break it all down heading into tonight's game. Sunday will also see a battle of first place teams (1:23) when the Packers take on the Colts. The Steelers remain the only unbeaten team in the NFL, but Ben Roethlisberger isn't worried about that, he has bigger goals in mind (2:47). Plus, the Vikings have been surging as of late, but quarterback Kirk Cousins says the team still has a long way to go (3:44)
